descriptionHtml:
Find, join, and host your group on Uplift.

1. Meet others who are in your shoes

3. Make friends for life

Private, easy to use, and ad-free.

Have questions, problems, or feedback? Reach out at hello@upliftgroups.com.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Version 2.1.4 includes various performance and user experience improvements across the app. Drop us a note at hello@upliftgroups.com if you have any comments or suggestions. Thanks for your continued support!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Version 3.0 of Uplift is here and introduces many exciting new features:

Audio:
Record and send audio clips within chats and as posts to a community feed.

Dark Mode:
The app's appearance will now correspond to your device's settings (either Light or Dark).

Message Pagination:
You can now scroll back to older messages in groups.

Photos and GIFs:
You can now post both Photos and GIFs to the community.

Performance:
Performance enhancements, making the app up to 3x as fast!
